rge.com/2023/10/30/23938990/bungie-sony-layoffs-delays-destiny- Final-shape-marathon&quot;>;上个月出现&lt;/a>;，原因是《Lightfall》发行反响不佳，导致《命运 2》玩家人数减少，Bungie 开始在工作室裁员。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;iMrYRd&quot;>;Bungie &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/30/23938990/bungie-sony-layoffs-delays-destiny-final-shape-马拉松“据报道解雇了大约 8% 的 Bungie 员工，影响了社区管理、工程、社交媒体、质量保证等方面的角色。现在，在《Lightfall》资料片受到负面评论和玩家情绪影响后，《光环》的创作者正在花时间完善《最终形态》。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;sM2YFc&quot;>;&lt;em>;最终形态&lt;/em>;是一个雄心勃勃的扩展包，旨在结束&lt;em>;命运&lt;/em>;的光明与黑暗传奇。 Bungie 几乎没有展示有关资料片的信息，因此...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/27/23943563/destiny-2-the-final- shape-delay-release-date-june-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/27/23943563/destiny-2-the-final-shape-delay-release-date-june-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/27/23943563/destiny-2-the-final-shape-delay-release-date-june-2024</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T12:17:15-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T12:17:15-05:00</updated><title>网络星期一 100 美元以下的最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;在 iPad Pro 上使用苹果第二代 Apple Pencil 的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/DiommkjYGiAXomf8s7Du1qR0iYo=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72892831/akrales_181101_3064_0171.10 .jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;第二代 Apple Pencil 的售价不到 100 美元。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ZNhyNu&quot;>;这是一年中最美好的时光？噗，更像是最贵的。礼物、旅行、装饰品、聚会、美味佳肴……这些都可以加起来让你的钱包省钱。这就是为什么我们努力以各种方式帮助您节省费用，从 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23951136/gifts-under-100-best-cheap-tech-ideas-2023-budget &quot;>;针对&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21587765/black-friday-cyber-monday-best-deals-how-to-find&quot;>;产品制定经济实惠的礼品指南&lt;/a>;寻找交易的技巧&lt;/a>;。现在，我们在下面汇总了 100 美元以下的最佳网络星期一优惠 — 其中许多是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas -unique-tech-gadgets&quot;>;我们的礼品指南中的特色内容&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;k8loXn&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;25 美元以下可获得的最佳网络星期一优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23971355/black-friday-2023-tech-deals -under-25-cyber-monday&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 50 美元以下节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23952179/tech-gifts-under-50 -best-cheap-ideas-2023-budget&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 25 美元以下节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23874403/tech-gifts-under -25-best-cheap-ideas-stocking-stuffers-2023-budget&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;zqcCCP&quot;>;我们发现了一系列打折的小玩意，从乐高到 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Fitbit-Exercise-Equipment-6-Months-Membership/dp/B0CC62ZG1M?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;poned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Fitbit Charge 6&lt;/a>; 至 &lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A %2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Ffujifilm-instax-mini-12-camera-mint-green%2F-%2FA-88075516&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; >;Fujifilm Instax Mini 12&lt;/a>; 甚至一对 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Apple-AirPods-Charging-Latest-Model/dp/B07PXGQC1Q?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel =&quot;赞助的 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;AirPods&lt;/a>;。不过，还有一些优惠可以帮助您节省其他费用，例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965708/black-friday-2023-streaming-deals-max-paramount-plus-hulu -cyber-monday&quot;>;流媒体服务&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;sWlCLk&quot;>;为了让您的生活更轻松，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/23965961/black-friday-2023-tech-deals-under-100-cyber-monday&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23965961/black-friday-2023-tech-deals-under-100-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23965961/black-friday-2023-tech-deals-under-100-cyber-monday</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T11:43:26-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T11:43:26-05:00</updated><title>数字车钥匙就在这里。我们准备好了吗？</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;数字车钥匙开门&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/OR_5qmpeVunpUvRPbbgRKaBxkiA=/0x1:3000x2001/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/ chorus_image/image/72906067/P90354782_highRes_bmw_digital_key_06_2.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：宝马&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;7T6nfn&quot;>;首先我们有手摇曲柄。然后是真正的钥匙，然后是钥匙扣。现在我们有了“数字钥匙”，您可以通过手机锁定、解锁和启动汽车。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;eNuMvb&quot;>;数字钥匙仍然很少见，仅在少数型号中提供。在数字密钥技术普及之前，还有很多问题需要解决。应使用哪种技术：近场通信 (NFC)？超宽带（UWB）？蓝牙？我们如何确保它免受黑客攻击？当你的手机电池没电时会发生什么？ （剧透：它仍然可以工作。）&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;xEdD9s&quot;>;许多汽车制造商已经提供数字钥匙，但它并不总是能完美地工作。特斯拉表示只会为 Model 3 提供数字钥匙，但后来选择了......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23970875/digital-car- key-iphone-unlock-start-ccc-standard&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23970875/digital-car-key-iphone-unlock-start-ccc-standard" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23970875/digital-car-key-iphone-unlock-start-ccc-standard</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T11:38:24-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T11:38:24-05:00</updated><title> Roomba 最新机器人吸尘器网络星期一最高立减 400 美元</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/XBt4mBTqJEESqqR2L4H43sqNQ1I=/0x0:5760x3840/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72903445 /8A0A0511.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;iRobot 的旗舰扫地机器人 j9 Combo Plus 网络星期一优惠 400 美元。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Jennifer Pattison Tuohy / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;4Rgsy2&quot;>;与 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/23/23973681/amazons -irobot-acquisition-likely-to-get-big-thumbs-up-from-eu&quot;>;新主人即将到来&lt;/a>;，iRobot 已经通过今年降低其全新吸尘器的价格进入亚马逊折扣游戏网络星期一。周五，它开始推出新的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/28/23845899/irobot-roomba-combo-j5-plus-robot-vacuum-mop-price&quot;>;预算和中档产品线&lt;/a>;、Roomba Combo i5 Plus 和 Combo j5 Plus，周日，iRobot 将其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/11/23864923 降价 400 美元/irobot-roomba-combo-j9-plus-robot-vacuum-mop-price-features&quot;>;全新顶级型号&lt;/a>;：j9 Plus 和 Combo j9 Plus。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;2mIqaI&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;亚马逊购买了 iRobot 来查看您的房屋内部&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23293687/amazon-irobot-acquisition-purchase-smarthome-intelligence-隐私分析&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Roomba j7 Plus 评论：现在顶部有拖把&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23489768/irobot-roomba-combo-j7- plus-robot-vacuum-mop-review&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;6mIW22&quot;>;Roomba j9 Plus 是该公司的新款旗舰扫地机器人，现已发售&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/iRobot-Roomba-Self-Emptying-Robot-Vacuum/dp/B0C415NHBM/?tag=theverge02- 售价 599 美元，&lt;strong>; &lt;/strong>;低于 899 美元20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/ck5siAuIR75&quot;>;百思买&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot; https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wellbots.com%2Fproducts%2Firobot-roomba-j9-robot-vacuum&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp; sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F11%2F26%2F23976565%2Firobot-roomba-j9-j5-i5-robot-vacuum-cyber-monday-deal“rel =“赞助nofollow noopener”目标=&q